VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT @Query\s*\(\s*"[^"]*(?::\w+|\?)[^"]*"\s*\)|SupportSQLiteDatabase.*compileStatement
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:@Query\s*\(\s*"[^"]*(?::\w+|\?)[^"]*"\s*\)|SupportSQLiteDatabase.*compileStatement && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Room or SQLite query patterns that use bound parameters instead of dynamic SQL interpolation.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Mitigation Identified: SQL Injection (Room Database).
